 20Ôćĺ    20Ôćĺ+# Guild Events Design
 21Ôćĺ    21Ôćĺ+
 22Ôćĺ    22Ôćĺ+Handle SMSG_GUILD_EVENT (0x0092) ÔÇö a read-only opcode that broadcasts guild
 23Ôćĺ    23Ôćĺ+activity notifications (promotions, sign-ons, MOTD changes, etc.) to online
 24Ôćĺ    24Ôćĺ+guild members.
 25Ôćĺ    25Ôćĺ+
 26Ôćĺ    26Ôćĺ+## Packet Structure
 27Ôćĺ    27Ôćĺ+
 28Ôćĺ    28Ôćĺ+From AzerothCore source (GuildPackets.cpp):
 29Ôćĺ    29Ôćĺ+
 30Ôćĺ    30Ôćĺ+```
 31Ôćĺ    31Ôćĺ+u8   eventType      GuildEvents enum (0-19)
 32Ôćĺ    32Ôćĺ+u8   paramCount     number of string params (0-3)
 33Ôćĺ    33Ôćĺ+CString[paramCount] event-specific string parameters
 34Ôćĺ    34Ôćĺ+u64LE guid          only present for JOINED/LEFT/SIGNED_ON/SIGNED_OFF
 35Ôćĺ    35Ôćĺ+```
 36Ôćĺ    36Ôćĺ+
 37Ôćĺ    37Ôćĺ+## Scope
 38Ôćĺ    38Ôćĺ+
 39Ôćĺ    39Ôćĺ+Social events only ÔÇö tabard, rank admin, and bank events are silently ignored.
 40Ôćĺ    40Ôćĺ+
 41Ôćĺ    41Ôćĺ+| Event (enum)       | Params                | Trailing GUID | Display |
 42Ôćĺ    42Ôćĺ+| ------------------ | --------------------- | ------------- | ------- |
 43Ôćĺ    43Ôćĺ+| PROMOTION (0)      | officer, member, rank | no            | yes     |
 44Ôćĺ    44Ôćĺ+| DEMOTION (1)       | officer, member, rank | no            | yes     |
 45Ôćĺ    45Ôćĺ+| MOTD (2)           | text                  | no            | yes     |
 46Ôćĺ    46Ôćĺ+| JOINED (3)         | name                  | yes           | yes     |
 47Ôćĺ    47Ôćĺ+| LEFT (4)           | name                  | yes           | yes     |
 48Ôćĺ    48Ôćĺ+| REMOVED (5)        | member, officer       | no            | yes     |
 49Ôćĺ    49Ôćĺ+| LEADER_IS (6)      | name                  | no            | yes     |
 50Ôćĺ    50Ôćĺ+| LEADER_CHANGED (7) | oldLeader, newLeader  | no            | yes     |
 51Ôćĺ    51Ôćĺ+| DISBANDED (8)      | (none)                | no            | yes     |
 52Ôćĺ    52Ôćĺ+| TABARD_CHANGED (9) | ÔÇö                     | ÔÇö             | ignored |
 53Ôćĺ    53Ôćĺ+| RANK_UPDATED (10)  | ÔÇö                     | ÔÇö             | ignored |
 54Ôćĺ    54Ôćĺ+| RANK_DELETED (11)  | ÔÇö                     | ÔÇö             | ignored |
 55Ôćĺ    55Ôćĺ+| SIGNED_ON (12)     | name                  | yes           | yes     |
 56Ôćĺ    56Ôćĺ+| SIGNED_OFF (13)    | name                  | yes           | yes     |
 57Ôćĺ    57Ôćĺ+| 14-19 (bank)       | ÔÇö                     | ÔÇö             | ignored |
 58Ôćĺ    58Ôćĺ+
 59Ôćĺ    59Ôćĺ+## Approach
 60Ôćĺ    60Ôćĺ+
 61Ôćĺ    61Ôćĺ+Expand the existing `GuildEvent` discriminated union in `guild-store.ts`.
 62Ôćĺ    62Ôćĺ+Reuse the existing `onGuildEvent` callback pipeline through WorldHandle,
 63Ôćĺ    63Ôćĺ+server.ts, ring buffer, and session log. No new callbacks or wiring needed.
 64Ôćĺ    64Ôćĺ+
 65Ôćĺ    65Ôćĺ+## GuildEvent Union
 66Ôćĺ    66Ôćĺ+
 67Ôćĺ    67Ôćĺ+```ts
 68Ôćĺ    68Ôćĺ+type GuildEvent =
 69Ôćĺ    69Ôćĺ+  | { type: "guild-roster"; roster: GuildRoster }
 70Ôćĺ    70Ôćĺ+  | { type: "promotion"; officer: string; member: string; rank: string }
 71Ôćĺ    71Ôćĺ+  | { type: "demotion"; officer: string; member: string; rank: string }
 72Ôćĺ    72Ôćĺ+  | { type: "motd"; text: string }
