 20Ôćĺ+# Guild Events Design
 21Ôćĺ+
 22Ôćĺ+Handle SMSG_GUILD_EVENT (0x0092) ÔÇö a read-only opcode that broadcasts guild
 23Ôćĺ+activity notifications (promotions, sign-ons, MOTD changes, etc.) to online
 24Ôćĺ+guild members.
 25Ôćĺ+
 26Ôćĺ+## Packet Structure
 27Ôćĺ+
 28Ôćĺ+From AzerothCore source (GuildPackets.cpp):
 29Ôćĺ+
 30Ôćĺ+```
 31Ôćĺ+u8   eventType      GuildEvents enum (0-19)
 32Ôćĺ+u8   paramCount     number of string params (0-3)
 33Ôćĺ+CString[paramCount] event-specific string parameters
 34Ôćĺ+u64LE guid          only present for JOINED/LEFT/SIGNED_ON/SIGNED_OFF
 35Ôćĺ+```
 36Ôćĺ+
 37Ôćĺ+## Scope
 38Ôćĺ+
 39Ôćĺ+Social events only ÔÇö tabard, rank admin, and bank events are silently ignored.
 40Ôćĺ+
 41Ôćĺ+| Event (enum)       | Params                | Trailing GUID | Display |
 42Ôćĺ+| ------------------ | --------------------- | ------------- | ------- |
 43Ôćĺ+| PROMOTION (0)      | officer, member, rank | no            | yes     |
 44Ôćĺ+| DEMOTION (1)       | officer, member, rank | no            | yes     |
 45Ôćĺ+| MOTD (2)           | text                  | no            | yes     |
 46Ôćĺ+| JOINED (3)         | name                  | yes           | yes     |
 47Ôćĺ+| LEFT (4)           | name                  | yes           | yes     |
 48Ôćĺ+| REMOVED (5)        | member, officer       | no            | yes     |
 49Ôćĺ+| LEADER_IS (6)      | name                  | no            | yes     |
 50Ôćĺ+| LEADER_CHANGED (7) | oldLeader, newLeader  | no            | yes     |
 51Ôćĺ+| DISBANDED (8)      | (none)                | no            | yes     |
 52Ôćĺ+| TABARD_CHANGED (9) | ÔÇö                     | ÔÇö             | ignored |
 53Ôćĺ+| RANK_UPDATED (10)  | ÔÇö                     | ÔÇö             | ignored |
 54Ôćĺ+| RANK_DELETED (11)  | ÔÇö                     | ÔÇö             | ignored |
 55Ôćĺ+| SIGNED_ON (12)     | name                  | yes           | yes     |
 56Ôćĺ+| SIGNED_OFF (13)    | name                  | yes           | yes     |
 57Ôćĺ+| 14-19 (bank)       | ÔÇö                     | ÔÇö             | ignored |
 58Ôćĺ+
 59Ôćĺ+## Approach
 60Ôćĺ+
 61Ôćĺ+Expand the existing `GuildEvent` discriminated union in `guild-store.ts`.
 62Ôćĺ+Reuse the existing `onGuildEvent` callback pipeline through WorldHandle,
 63Ôćĺ+server.ts, ring buffer, and session log. No new callbacks or wiring needed.
 64Ôćĺ+
 65Ôćĺ+## GuildEvent Union
 66Ôćĺ+
 67Ôćĺ+```ts
 68Ôćĺ+type GuildEvent =
 69Ôćĺ+  | { type: "guild-roster"; roster: GuildRoster }
 70Ôćĺ+  | { type: "promotion"; officer: string; member: string; rank: string }
 71Ôćĺ+  | { type: "demotion"; officer: string; member: string; rank: string }
 72Ôćĺ+  | { type: "motd"; text: string }
 73Ôćĺ+  | { type: "joined"; name: string }
 74Ôćĺ+  | { type: "left"; name: string }
 75Ôćĺ+  | { type: "removed"; member: string; officer: string }
 76Ôćĺ+  | { type: "leader_is"; name: string }
 77Ôćĺ+  | { type: "leader_changed"; oldLeader: string; newLeader: string }
 78Ôćĺ+  | { type: "disbanded" }
 79Ôćĺ+  | { type: "signed_on"; name: string }
 80Ôćĺ+  | { type: "signed_off"; name: string };
 81Ôćĺ+```
 82Ôćĺ+
 83Ôćĺ+## Text Formatting
 84Ôćĺ+
 85Ôćĺ+All displayed with `[guild]` prefix:
 86Ôćĺ+
 87Ôćĺ+- promotion: `[guild] Officer promoted Member to Rank`
 88Ôćĺ+- demotion: `[guild] Officer demoted Member to Rank`
 89Ôćĺ+- motd: `[guild] MOTD: text`
 90Ôćĺ+- joined: `[guild] Name has joined the guild`
 91Ôćĺ+- left: `[guild] Name has left the guild`
 92Ôćĺ+- removed: `[guild] Officer removed Member from the guild`
 93Ôćĺ+- leader_is: `[guild] Name is the guild leader`
 94Ôćĺ+- leader_changed: `[guild] OldLeader has made NewLeader the new guild leader`
 95Ôćĺ+- disbanded: `[guild] Guild has been disbanded`
 96Ôćĺ+- signed_on: `[guild] Name has come online`
 97Ôćĺ+- signed_off: `[guild] Name has gone offline`
 98Ôćĺ+
 99Ôćĺ+## JSON Formatting
100Ôćĺ+
101Ôćĺ+Each event maps to a typed object for structured logging:
102Ôćĺ+
103Ôćĺ+```ts
104Ôćĺ+{
105Ôćĺ+  type: ("GUILD_PROMOTION", officer, member, rank);
106Ôćĺ+}
107Ôćĺ+{
108Ôćĺ+  type: ("GUILD_DEMOTION", officer, member, rank);
109Ôćĺ+}
110Ôćĺ+{
111Ôćĺ+  type: ("GUILD_MOTD", text);
112Ôćĺ+}
113Ôćĺ+{
114Ôćĺ+  type: ("GUILD_JOINED", name);
115Ôćĺ+}
116Ôćĺ+{
117Ôćĺ+  type: ("GUILD_LEFT", name);
118Ôćĺ+}
119Ôćĺ+{
120Ôćĺ+  type: ("GUILD_REMOVED", member, officer);
121Ôćĺ+}
122Ôćĺ+{
123Ôćĺ+  type: ("GUILD_LEADER_IS", name);
124Ôćĺ+}
125Ôćĺ+{
126Ôćĺ+  type: ("GUILD_LEADER_CHANGED", oldLeader, newLeader);
127Ôćĺ+}
128Ôćĺ+{
129Ôćĺ+  type: "GUILD_DISBANDED";
130Ôćĺ+}
131Ôćĺ+{
132Ôćĺ+  type: ("GUILD_SIGNED_ON", name);
133Ôćĺ+}
134Ôćĺ+{
135Ôćĺ+  type: ("GUILD_SIGNED_OFF", name);
136Ôćĺ+}
137Ôćĺ+```
