155Ôćĺ+# Guild Events Implementation Plan
156Ôćĺ+
157Ôćĺ+> **For Claude:** REQUIRED SUB-SKILL: Use superpowers:executing-plans to implement this plan task-by-task.
158Ôćĺ+
159Ôćĺ+**Goal:** Handle SMSG_GUILD_EVENT (0x0092) to display guild activity notifications as system messages.
160Ôćĺ+
161Ôćĺ+**Architecture:** Expand the existing `GuildEvent` union with 11 new variants, add a packet parser, wire a handler through the existing `onGuildEvent` callback pipeline, and add text/JSON formatters. TDD throughout.
162Ôćĺ+
163Ôćĺ+**Tech Stack:** TypeScript, Bun test runner, PacketReader/PacketWriter
164Ôćĺ+
165Ôćĺ+---
166Ôćĺ+
167Ôćĺ+### Task 1: Parser ÔÇö parseGuildEvent
168Ôćĺ+
